Description: Zomick's Kosher Bakery is a consumer bakery goods provider company.
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Zomick's kosher bakery is one of the most popular bakeries in New York. Why? Well, because it sets groundbreaking new standards on a well known product line, and nobody can beat that. The fact that Zomick's bakery was founded back in 1966, shows that this small bakery exists now for about 50 years... years of tradition, years of experience. Zomick’s is leader in kosher bakery business in New York. Its beginnings date from the late 60’s when David Jonson and his wife started their small bakery business.  As the time was passing, the demand for their kosher bakery products was constantly growing. This was due to the fact that everything baked in Zomick’s bakery was real kosher food, following the Jewish tradition of making bread all incorporated in the traditional Zomick's Challah recipe. Nowadays, Zomick’s kosher bakery is serving the wide Jewish community in New York with the highest quality baked goods, which are made in accordance to the highest standards of kashruth. You don't need to be Jewish to fall in love with Zomick’s bread being produced from a long-time fixture on Fifth Avenue, New York, that truly lives up to its "more than a bakery" tagline. Zomick’s product list varies from different types of kosher bread, such as challah and delicious chocolate babka to bagels, doughnuts and variety of pastries and cakes. A fine team of bakers is dedicated to providing the best quality of kosher bakery goods. When you enter the Zomick’s bakery store for the first time, what sends you to heaven and back is the aroma of fresh-baked Zomick's bread, displayed behind the counter, including magnificent braided loaves and rolls baked by the direction of Zomick’s challah recipes; best-selling plain and seeded rye, corn rye, and onion rye, and authentic, old-style bagels and bialys. Zomick’s kosher bakery is known for its wide and diverse array of baking goods such as breads, cakes, and fine pastries. We bake everything fresh and kosher using only the finest ingredients, ensuring the clients the certainty to enjoy the most scrumptious selection of kosher baked goods that can be found in New York. If you want to be sure in your choice, if you want to eat a real kosher food without doubts whether it is the kosher food you are really looking for, visit Zomick’s kosher bakery store.
